<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢١٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ بِالْمَدِينَةِ فَزَعٌ فَرَكِبَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَرَسًا لِأَبِي طَلْحَةَ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> مَا رَأَيْنَا مِنْ شَيْءٍ، وَإِنْ وَجَدْنَاهُ لَبَحْرًا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>